         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <ab>(Sacred?) to the Shades of the Dead. Greetings to you, traveller! If you wish to identify my inscription, I was Nigrio (?) Aequidicus. I was healthy while I was alive, and I fared well. I devoted happy years to Bacchus and to slumber. Ah, a wretch! A brief hour carried off so many things(?). (Farewell!)</ab>
